.TH "GAMEPAD.MAPPING" "3JS" "December 27, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
Gamepad.mapping \- Gamepad: mapping property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]Gamepad.mapping\f[B]\f[R] property of the
\f[CR]Gamepad\f[R] interface returns a string indicating whether the
browser has remapped the controls on the device to a known layout.
.PP
The currently supported known layouts are:
.IP \(bu 2
\(lqstandard\(rq for the \c
.UR https://w3c.github.io/gamepad/#remapping
standard gamepad
.UE \c
\&.
.IP \(bu 2
\(lqxr\-standard for the \c
.UR https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr-gamepads-module/#xr-standard-heading
standard XR gamepad
.UE \c
\&.
See also \f[CR]XRInputSource.gamepad\f[R].
.SH EXAMPLES
.IP
.EX
\f[B]let\f[R] gp = navigator.getGamepads()[0];
console.log(gp.mapping);
.EE
.SH SEE ALSO
Using the Gamepad API
